</div></div><section class="section" id="parameters-20"><h3 class="anchorable-heading">Parameters <a href="#parameters-20" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a></h3><div class="space-y-8"><div class="anchorable docEntry" id="function_session_prototype_post_20_parameters_method"><div class="docEntryHeader"><code class><a href="#function_session_prototype_post_20_parameters_method" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a><span class="font-bold font-lg">method</span><span class="font-medium"><span>: <span>"Debugger.setSkipAllPauses"</span></span></span></code> </div></div><div class="anchorable docEntry" id="function_session_prototype_post_20_parameters_params"><div class="docEntryHeader"><code class><a href="#function_session_prototype_post_20_parameters_params" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a><span class="font-bold font-lg">params</span><span class="font-medium"><span>: <a href="../../.././inspector/promises/~/Debugger.SetSkipAllPausesParameterType" class="link">Debugger.SetSkipAllPausesParameterType</a></span></span></code> <span><div class="text-optional border border-optional/50 bg-optional/5 inline-flex items-center gap-0.5 flex-none rounded-md leading-none text-sm py-1 px-2">optional</div></span></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="return-type-20"><h3 class="anchorable-heading">Return Type <a href="#return-type-20" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a></h3><div class="space-y-8"><div class=" docEntry" id="function_Session_prototype_post_20_return"><div class="docEntryHeader"><code class><span class="font-medium"><span>Promise</span>&lt;<span>void</span>&gt;</span></code> </div></div></div></section></div></div><h2>Overload 22</h2><div class="scroll-mt-16" id="function_Session_prototype_post_21"><code class="anchorable break-words inline-code-block"><a href="#function_Session_prototype_post_21" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a><s