</div></div><section class="section" id="parameters-77"><h3 class="anchorable-heading">Parameters <a href="#parameters-77" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a></h3><div class="space-y-8"><div class="anchorable docEntry" id="function_session_prototype_post_77_parameters_method"><div class="docEntryHeader"><code class><a href="#function_session_prototype_post_77_parameters_method" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a><span class="font-bold font-lg">method</span><span class="font-medium"><span>: <span>"Network.enable"</span></span></span></code> </div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="return-type-77"><h3 class="anchorable-heading">Return Type <a href="#return-type-77" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a></h3><div class="space-y-8"><div class=" docEntry" id="function_Session_prototype_post_77_return"><div class="docEntryHeader"><code class><span class="font-medium"><span>Promise</span>&lt;<span>void</span>&gt;</span></code> </div></div></div></section></div></div><h2>Overload 79</h2><div class="scroll-mt-16" id="function_Session_prototype_post_78"><code class="anchorable break-words inline-code-block"><a href="#function_Session_prototype_post_78" class="anchor-link" aria-label="Anchor" tabindex="-1">#</a><span class="font-bold">Session.prototype.post</span><span class="font-medium">(<span><span>method<span>: <span>"NodeRuntime.enable"</span></span></span></span>)<span>: <span>Promise</span>&lt;<span>void</span>&gt;</span></span></code><div class="space-y-7" id><div><div data-color-mode="dark" data-light-theme="light" data-dark-theme="dark" class="markdown-body"><p>Enable the NodeRuntime events except by <code>NodeRuntime.waitingForDisconnect</code>.</p>
